danielachalbaud.description: Daniela Xanadu Chalbaud is a model, actress and activist from Venezuela that wan the Miss Intercontinental 2012 title, being the fifth Venezuelan to reach the crown of Miss Intercontinental. Continuing the competition Daniela Chalbaud began to build her modeling career in South America, the Caribbean, the Middle East and Europe performing campaigns and editorials such as Emmi-Dent, Emmi-Nail, Steighenberger Resort, Coca-Cola, Wrangler, Head & Shoulders, Poett and music videos. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

rachel_mortenson.description: Rachel Marie Mortenson is a model with an international career. Her work experience includes modeling for numerous known brands including Frederick's of Hollywood - Costume Shop, Clothing, Lingerie & Sleepwear. Having started in her home state as a waitress and calendar girl for Hooters. Since then she has been featured multiple times including a Carl’s Jr. commercial, and also on the cover of Playboy’s recent Sex & Music issue and also becoming the beautiful face of Guess’s high-end Marciano line. She had featured her own ten-page spread in the January 2015 issue of Playboy. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

alliemaebb.description: Allie Leggett is a model from Kentucky. She has been titled Miss Kentuky USA - 2013. Her work experience includes modeling for numerous brands and designers. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

carrielynna.description: Carrie Amstutz is a model based in Florida. Her work experience includes photoshoots for numerous publications. She is also a writer and a soap maker. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

rincityofficial.description: Katrina Wilkinson (Rin) is a model and College student based in Las Vegas. Art is her passion and she works hard to become better, her interests include reading, drawing, singing and sculpting while her modeling work has been featured in several publications. She is known for her quiet and lovable character. She likes to "play dress-up" and try different styles. She wants to extend her skills in art to all mediums, including modeling. She is available for fashion and print projects.

viviankindle.description: Vivian Kindle was born in Easter Washington, Wenatchee, raised in the small town of Bellingham WA. Her mothers decent is European and Indonesian, her father is Czechoslovakian and French. Vivian started modeling at the age of sixteen, her passion, drive and ambition drove her to a very successful career and exciting life! Working with several local photographers she began to build her portfolio which immediately lead her to a few publications and travels. Promotional modeling became a big part of her career, she worked with companies such a RockStar, Monster, UmbrellaGirlsUSA, Playboy fight night MMA, SEMA, DUB, and Harley Davidson.

hannajoy078.description: Hanna Joy is a Spanish-Filipino model, who was born in the Philippines and grew up in Papua New Guinea. She has always had a deep passion for modeling, fashion, and travel. Hanna Joy also has a love for photography. She believes that fashion and photography combined is an astounding work of art and creativity. She believes that modeling is an expressive art form seeing that it shows movement and feelings in a still photo. Hanna Joy is available for fashion and print projects as well as collaboration with other modeling professionals.

samanthaamodel_.description: Samantha Autum is professional model based in Riverside,CA. Her work experience includes numerous publications for magazines, websites, books and calendars. She is also does promotional work & Host events. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

sphammytkd.description: Stephanie Andrea Pham is a multi-talented individual that models, acts, and studies martial arts. Currently studying under the tutelage of Mr. Kenneth John McGregor at the Walking Fish Theatre, Ms. Pham aspires to be a strong actress in the film and television industry.

missdanimathers.description: Dani Mathers is a model and actress who is the Playboy Playmate of the Month for May 2014. Since 2005, she has appeared in a recurring role (as "Danica") on the CBS soap opera The Bold and the Beautiful. She has also been a Playboy CyberGirl of the Month in January 2013 and appeared on the cover of Playboy Girls of Summer, and she has also appeared on Playboy TV’s Badass, Playboy Trip: Patagonia, Playboy’s Beach House and Camp Playboy.

laurenkvickers.description: Lauren Vickers is an Australian born and bred model with over 16 years experience in the modelling industry. Best known for her relationship with Playboy, she was named 2010-11 Playmate of the Year by Playboy Italia and Playmate of the month for January 2012 by Playboy España. She is also a motorcycle rider, animal lover, TV Presenter and wife of French MotoGP rider Randy de Puniet.

cmarusanici.description: Claudia Marusanici is a Romanian model currently based in New York. Claudia is an international model having worked throughout US and Europe. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots for fashion and lingerie catalogs as well as runway shows. Claudia also holds a Bachelor’s Degree in Communication and Media Studies and has worked on the Image of several well-known brands such as New Balance, Exhale Spa New York and Vaseline, developing along the way excellent working partnerships with key individuals in the Fashion industry. She speaks Romanian, English as well as Italian, Spanish and Ukrainian. She is also a skilled makeup artist as involved into photography herself. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

mabelynncapeluj.description: Mabelynn Capeluj is a model born and raised in sunny San Diego. Additionally to modeling she has been studying broadcast journalism at Chapman University. After she obtains her Master’s degree, Mabelynn aspires to work for E! News as an Entertainment Reporter. Her modeling experience includes campaigns for known brands including Miami Swim and Sketchers. Being a big sister to six younger brother she is very active and enjoys outdoor activities such as jet skiing and rock climbing. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

courtneyoconnor.description: Courtney O'Connor is a model based in Miami, Florida. Courtney has international modeling experience which includes among others modeling at Mercedes Benz Fashion Week in New York and Miami for designers such as Tadashi Shoji, Toni Fransesc, Catherine Malandrino, Malan Breton, Chado Ralph Rucci, Sashika Twins, Luli Fama, Caffe Swimwear, and Maaji. She has been the face of Swim N Sport, Corioliss Hair, Reitman's, Bluefish Sport, Invicta Watches and more. She has been featured in several magazines such as Vogue Italia, Vogue France, Elle, and GQ.

erikamyrvik.description: Erika Joy Myrvik is a model based in Los Angeles, CA. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots for brands and designers. She is available for fashion and print projects.

iamjlynne.description: J Lynne is a new model in Zürich, coming from America she is a Swiss citizen as well as a US citizen for work purposes. She is currently represented by Reinhard Agency - Philadelphia.

maddieosully.description: Madeline O'Sullivan is an agency signed model from Atlanta currently traveling between Atlanta and Milan, Italy. Available for fashion and print projects internationally.

brittanymasonofficial.description: Brittany Mason is a model, actress, activist, author and producer. Her vast experience includes runway, commercial, print, television, and has traveled and lived internationally in Europe, Asia, and all across the USA. She has also appeared on the popular American television show Two and a Half Men where she played Janeane, guest star Jason Alexander's mistress and secretary.

penelopeainhoa.description: Penelope Heilmann is a German/Spanish model currently based in NYC. Her work experience includes modeling for numerous brands and designers in NY, Paris, Milan and London. Penelope speaks English, German, Portuguese and Spanish. Highly experienced and trained she is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

sarahstage.description: Sarah Stage is an exotic ethnic background of Costa Rican & European. As a Los Angeles native, Sarah Stage grew up with her parents and younger sister in Burbank, California. Living in "the Media Capitol of the World" motivated Sarah to pursue her dream of modeling and acting. While attending high school she decided to enter an Elite Models Search and was a runner up. From there Sarah headed to Milan, Italy where she furthered her career as a high fashion model. Since then she has done several national print campaigns, runway shows, tv shows, commercials and spokesmodel jobs. Outside of the busy world of show business, Sarah enjoys oil painting, traveling over seas, salsa dancing and being an active animal rights activist. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

kyleighmccollam.description: Kyleigh Mccollam is a professional model and aspiring high fashion designer. Acting, dancing, skimboarding, and snowboarding are a few things she enjoys doing on her spare time. She loves skim-boarding, snowboarding, and is going to school to pursue fashion design. Her work experience includes working with photographers such as Kaunis Hetki, Michael Afonso and Gina Biallo as well as some publications. She is available for fashion and print projects.

josie_dawn.description: Josie Barton is a model based in Saint Louis, Missouri. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots as well as participation in events. She has performed as a runway model and has also appeared in magazine covers. Available for fashion and print projects.

janaknauer.description: Jana Knauerova is a Czech Fashion model. As a model her work experience includes numerous photoshoots and publications. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

hopebeel.description: Hope Beel is a model and athlete based in Dallas, TX She is also a health and wellness coach. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots and promotional events from fitness modeling to high fashion. Always up to new and exciting work, she loves fashion and modeling and is interested in collaborating with talented artists. She is available for fashion, print, and video projects.

chelseabpereira.description: Model And Actress is a model and actress from San Diego, Ca. As a model she has worked with companies like Neff, Make Up Forever, Def Jam, Wella, and more. As an actor she has appeared on television shows for NBC, Fox Sports, MTV, National Geographic, PBS, HDnet, the CW, commercials for Axe France, music videos for Calvin Harris, Nicki Minaj and Drop City Yacht Club, and a short films for Sony. Aside from her work in the entertainment industry, she studied at the Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising and majored in Marketing and Business for the Beauty Industry. She has a men's health and cooking blog called Healthy is Handsome. Her recipes are available at healthyishandsome. She hopes to eventually have her own skin care, supplement and color cosmetic company. In her free time she loves to cook, and used to teach classes at Williams-Sonoma, hip hop dance, yoga, pilates, and hike with her dog. She is available for fashion, print and acting projects internationally.

valeriasokolovaofficial.description: Valeria Sokolova is a Russian model currently located in Miami, FL. Her work experience includes multiple publications and participation in events. She is known for her hair, lips, and eyebrows. Originally from Penza, Russia. She had attended Penza State University there, as well as the Miami University. She is fluent in several languages: English, Russian, Italian, German, and French. Available for fashion and print projects internationally.

joannaborov.description: Joanna Borov is a Polish model living in the USA, California. Joanna was published in magazines like Playboy, Maxim, Vogue. She won World Beauty Queen Poland 2018 and Miss Motors Formula1 Silverstone 2018. She worked at London Fashion Week, Paris Fashion Week, LA Fashion Week, and many other notable events. She is also involved in interior design and art as well as health and fitness (author of a few publications about healthy lifestyle).

ariannyceleste.description: Arianny Celeste is a UFC Octagon ring girl, co-host to Overhaulin, Mtv Guy Code, Host, Model, & Fitness professional having made numerous TV appearances including Ultimate Fighter and promotions. Arianny Celeste was born on November 12 in Las Vegas Nevada. She booked her first modeling job when she was four months old for a car seat company. She has always been athletic excelling in cheer, dance, and gymnastics. Arianny started back into modeling at the age of 15. She attended UNLV majoring in fitness management and nutrition. In 2006 she was casted as the new UFC octagon girl. She has been with the company for over 5 years now and has seen it explode. She has appeared in many magazines including Playboy, FHM, Maxim, Maxim espanol and many more. She currently resides in Los Angeles where she has had the opportunity to be in films and music videos. One of her main passions is music. She loves to sing and has recorded some original songs. Another passion of hers is fitness. She loves to help others and finds it very rewarding.

tugbaercan.description: Tugba Ercan is a Turkish-born American model, TV personality and actress. She is known for her pleasant character, her work ethic and passion for fitness. Born and raised in Turkey, Tugba moved to the States in summer of ’96. Tugba graduated Magna Cum Laude before she focused solely on her modeling career. In love with the camera since she was a little girl, she has naturally grown into the roles she plays as a Brand Ambassador, and as a model for fashion shows, magazines, commercials, print, and music videos.

onyekaxo.description: Onyekachukwu is a free-spirited and ambitious Nigerian Model. Her specialty is in Print, Commercial, Editorial and Runway assignments. Her work includes photoshoots for multiple photographers and publications. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

laurenrebeccaroth.description: Lauren Rebecca Roth is a professional model based in Chicago. She is a student of Psychology and English and she has a background in musical theater and is very comfortable in front of the camera. Having spent plenty of time around fashion designers, Lauren has developed her own unique but vastly diverse style so she can lend it to those projects she’s hired for. When not attending class, traveling or networking online, she is making connections at fashion events around the city. Cooperative and outgoing, she is available for fashion and print projects as well as collaboration with other modeling professionals.

modelajknapp.description: AJ Knapp is a professional model based in the South Florida area. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots, participation is fashion shows, promotional events as well as dancing. AJ also practices martial arts, having a personal collection of martial art weapons and creative props. She has a vast selection of wardrobe and accessories that can be used for styling. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

karinium.description: Karina Dunaeva is a professional Model, Actress and Filmmaker currently based in Miami. She studied at the California State University of Los Angeles and speaks English and Russian. Her work experience includes numerous photo-shoots and she has worked in Canada, USA and Russia as a model. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

nicoledomecus.description: Nicole Domecus is an American born model and actress. She is represented by Wilhelmina New York. Her client list includes L'Oreal Paris, Guess, Levis, Dockers, Ariat, Hyundai, Samsung, Neiman Marcus, Old Navy, C. Wonder and many others. She has been featured on Sports Illustrated as LLOD. As an actress she is known for her participation in The Other Woman (2014), Horrible Bosses 2 (2014) and Scouted (2011). Available for fashion and print projects internationally.

ktrinaelizabeth.description: Katrina Elizabeth is a model, actress and writer (her book: Through My Eyes) based in Los Angeles. She was born and raised in Sonoma County, CA. She lived on the Russian river with acres of vineyards and went to college at Mills College in Oakland, CA. She has majored in Economics and graduated in 3 years and worked after graduation for Wells Fargo Bank as a Registered Premier Banker for over 4 years. She is a yoga, fitness, and health enthusiast, and also loves creating and capturing art. She is known for her thoughtful, loving, and adventurous personality while when she is not modeling, she likes painting, writing, drawing and yoga. She is available for fashion, print and acting projects internationally.

yevalova.description: Yeva took her first steps as a model by the age of 12 in Russia, there she went to a Russian model school. At the age of 15 Yeva left Russia and moved to Israel by herself. Yeva spent mostly in airports from her base in Tel Aviv to most of fashion capitals in the world : from Milan to Paris to New York to London and many many more. At the age of 18, when she was wanted for modeling jobs all over, Yeva decided to stop and to fulfill her duties as a proud Israeli and to join the Israeli army. In the army she served at Israeli defense services .and studied psychology and communications in The Open University of Israel.

alexis.hicks.description: Alexis Hicks is a Miami based model, specializing in fashion, swimwear, and beauty. Expanding into commercial TV and acting. She is traveling for projects, shoots, and workshops. Her work experience includes commercial assignments, glamour modeling and acting. She is available for fashion and print projects.

sabinakelley.description: Sabina Kelley has established herself as a true, modern day, pinup and icon. With a wide international presence, she has graced dozens of magazine covers as well as major ad campaigns, television, music videos, calendars, and so much more. She is highly respected in her field and has been sought out by some of the top photographers in the business including David LaChapelle and the legendary, Bunny Yeager.

reed_kr.description: Kristin Reed is a model based in Dallas, TX. Kristin Reed’s modeling work includes print, live modeling, commercial and TV advertising. Kristin is known to be highly active and love sports and fitness. She has also been a spokesperson as well as participated in TV and Commercials for NASCAR, The NFL network/Supebowl and such segments as Why visit' Community of SouthLake, TX, 'Good Morning Texas' Blaines Haircolor Segment and CNN 'Fatality the Gamer' Gaming Products. She is currently with The Campbell Agency and is available for fashion print, fitness and commercial assignments.

jhubbell93.description: Janessa Hubbell is a model based in White Lake, Michigan. She is known for fun personality as well as for her ability to take direction and cooperate well with others. Her work experience includes photoshoots and runway assignment. She is available for fashion and print projects.

juststephrai.description: Steph Rai is a model and actress based in New York. Her work experience includes photoshots for numerous publications as well as runway shows. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

aferditadreshaj.description: Afërdita Dreshaj is an Albanian-Kosovar public figure best known for being crowned Miss Universe Kosovo 2011 and representing the Republic of Kosovo in Miss Universe 2011. Dreshaj is a well-known singer in Albanian speaking countries, having debuted with her first single "Nëse Je Burrë" in 2009. She is available for commercial projects internationally.

anna.kin.la.description: Anna Kin is a model, dancer and choreographer from Belarus currently based in Los Angeles California. Her experience includes noumerous photoshoots for brands as well as participation in fashion shows. Known for her professionalism Anna is also very athletic with excellent training. She has been modeling since 2009. Jobs: Russia, Moscow - the model agency Fresh Models. Belarus, Minsk - the model agency Tamara Models Minsk. Milan, Italy - the model agency 2morrow Models.

karleyparker.description: Karley Parker is a model, artist & executive designer of Social Events for Scenemakers. Her work experience includes numerous photoshoots for designers. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

karensoto_official.description: Karen Soto-Salazar is an international model based in New York. Her work experience includes modeling for shows and events as well as fashion photoshoots. Managed by Wilhelmina New York City, she is available for fashion and print projects internationally. She was born in Cali, Colombian and since the start of her career she has model for Custo Barcelona, Agatha Ruiz de la Prada, Roberto Cavalli, Badgley Mischka, and many more. In 2017 she was part of the third season of Colombia’s next top model, she came fourth place in the competition, after her participation in the reality show she was signed by Wilhelmina Models and since then she’s been doing worldwide campaigns and commercials.

katarinavanderham.description: Katarina is a TV and Print model based in Hollywood, California. Independent Entertainment Professional. President & Editor-in-Chief of Viva Glam Magazine

bryantwoodtv.description: Bryant Wood is a Los Angeles, California based fitness and fashion model and actor. Bryan is an exercise specialist and has participated in numerous fashion photoshoots. Additionally to modeling Wood received an education at Grand Canyon University on a full ride wrestling scholarship, where he studied Business before realizing his place was the entertainment industry. Since then he has committed himself to multiple humanitarian causes, and often engages in various acts of charity in his spare time. He also has acting experience and among his recent recent roles is "This Just In" on Pop TV. Bryant Wood is a seasoned professional talent accepting fashion and editorial assignments worldwide.

smbayless.description: Shannon is an agency represented model originally from the midwest, now living in Los Angeles. Shannon's modeling career started at age 13 when she got signed with BMG Models Chicago. Since then, she has worked with noumerous talented photographers. She has been internationally published and done national campaigns for commercial brands such as Kohl's and Claire's. Not only limited to commercial modeling; she has experience in swimwear traveling to 7 different Caribbean islands to shoot for Hot Tropix. She has also graced the cover of Maxim France. From Bridal magazines, lingerie shoots, beauty spreads and live body paint events she has gathered experience & knowledge about the industry. Her full resume is available upon request. Shannon approaches every shoot as a professional. Although, she is mainly shooting in California now she is available to travel to other areas with travel expenses covered. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

meaghanmonaghan_.description: Born and raised in NYC, Meaghan has been professionally modeling since the age of 15. She has appeared in print, most recently Manhattan Bride. Not only does she have impressive tearsheets, she has rocked the runway for the President of Indonesia at the Waldorf Astoria, NYC for Fashion Week. In addition she is featured on a an electronic billboard for The FurSource located off the prestigious shopping district of 5th Avenue in Manhattan. Meaghan's modeling interest lay in lifestyle and commercial photography.

caitlin__oconnor.description: Caitlin O’Connor grew up in Pennsylvania, but was born in Los Angeles where she now resides. She was persuaded to enter scholarship pageants where she became a top finalist in the Miss Pennsylvania USA pageant. After this, she moved home to California to attend UCLA where she won a few pageant titles that ultimately led her to her future in modeling and acting with high profile campaigns and music videos to follow. She appeared in Maxim Magazine as both their “Helpful Hottie” advice girl and as one of the “Top Ten Hottest Girls in America” in 2014. Appearing in over 100 music videos as an actress or dancer, she has worked with notable artists such as Simple Plan, Miguel, Yelawolf, New Found Glory and Chris Brown, so you can say her talents are diverse and she can tackle pretty much anything. O’Connor has been a regular actress on the MTV series Chelsea Settles as well as a guest on shows like HBO’s Entourage and Comedy Central’s The Nick Kroll Show as well as Tosh.O. Caitlin appears in Sports Illustrated as their “Lovely Lady of the Day” three times, most recently in 2014. She spends her time and talent helping non-profit organizations geared towards kids and animals. She is also a classic car enthusiast collecting vintage Lincoln Continentals.

crystaltwinston.description: Crystal Toi Winston was born and raised in San Diego, California, she was discovered by the Worlds First Super Model, @Janice Dickinson and starred along side Janice on two seasons of The Janice Dickinson Model Agency which aired on the Oxygen network. In 2012, Crystal moved to Los Angeles to sign with Models International. Miss. Winston has graced the runways of Ed Hardy, Nicoletta Swim Wear, House of Estrada, Papyrus and has walked in both Miami and Los Angeles Fashion Week. In 2013, Crystal Winston stepped into the recording studio as has plans to release her EP rap album by then end of the year.

hey_marine1.description: Marine Guadalpi is a model from France currently living in Miami. She loves modeling with a passion and Wants to further her career. She has been modeling for four years. She is known to be an energetic person who always has a smile on her face. Professional and dedicated she is easy to work with and puts forth all her effort into each project to achieve the best results. She is available for fashion and print projects.

missashleysarina.description: Ashley Sarina Hoffmann is a fitness model based in Milwaukee, Wisconsin. She is a personal trainer and also a sponsored athlete for Cellucor/Neon Sport and Tainted Industries. Her work experience includes fitness, bikini and fashion photoshoots. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

valeria_orsini.description: Valeria Orsini is a Miami Colombian model on the rise. As an accomplished model and aspiring actress. she loves being in front of the camera and loves being around new and exciting people. She loves her family and tries to be the best at whatever she does. Valeria Orsini was born in Atlanta, Georgia January 19th, 1990 and lived there till the age of two. Later Moved to Miami Florida in which she was raised and still resides. She is of Colombian, Italian, and Puerto Rican descent who measures 34C-24-35. She is known to be smart, beautiful, determined, and Sassy at 5ft.2in. Valeria Orsini has done everything from calendars for “Latin Mix” to Swimming with sharks for “PlayBoy TV” and special guest on “Bunny Talk Radio”. 2010 May’s cover of Nine5Four magazine also Graced the cover of 2010 September’s Mixed Magazine. She has walked the runway live for Tara Love, Linda Zamora, Lace to Lust and more. Has hosted some of the hottest clubs across America and has featured in numerous videos for artist like Trina, Flo rida, Cam’ron, and Mon E.G. She is driven and coming up in distinction in several areas of the modeling world; such as featuring in magazines, radio, TV programs and commercials and numerous music videos.

barbarella_desiree.description: Barbara Desiree Kovach is an internationally published glamour model based out of Cleveland, Ohio. She has been modeling professionally since July/August of 2012. She is a traveling model and during her work she had the pleasure to visit interesting places. She had studied theatre and arts before modeling full time and worked on various shows in Lakeland Community Theatre for three years. Kirtland, Ohio participating in acting, set design and costume design. She is known for her professionalism, flexibility and passion for her work. She is available for promotional, print, portfolio, and advertising work. Also available for one on one shoots, workshops and campaigns.

raeeexoxo.description: Raven Forrester started modeling at age 11, with her first agency being Williams Talent in Sugar Land, TX. At the age of 19, she signed with Neal Hamil Agency in Houston and Avant Agency in San Antonio. In 2014, Raven signed to Wilhelmina Austin (now known as Brown Agency) and Model Management Group (MMG) in New York. She is also represented by BEAZ Talent in Houston TX. Raven frequently travels for work and has worked for brands such as Nike, Verizon, New Era, Baby Phat & Kimora Lee Simmons Collection, Calia by Carrie Underwood, Magnolia Silks, Samsung, Microsoft, and many more. Raven's runway experience includes multiple seasons at New York Fashion Week and Paris Fashion Week.

ellionita.description: Elena Kollarova is a model originally from Cherven Bryag, Bulgaria but now resides in Boston, MA. She has been the winner of Miss Bulgarka 2013 in USA by People's Choice and Crowned 1st Runner-up by the Judges. Winner of Boston's Best Female Runway Model Award for 2012. After graduating with a golden medal for academic excellence from the National High School of Mathematics and Sciences in Sofia, she pursued her college education at Suffolk University, where she graduated with Cum Laude Latin honors receiving a Bachelor of Science in Biology/Marine Science and Chemistry. In 2010 Elena became a NAUI certified SCUBA Diver and is currently training for an Advanced Diving certification.

tara_grace.description: Tara Grace Elizabeth is a professional model based in Hawaii. She has also worked in California, Thailand and France. She is experienced and has worked with brands such as Harry Winston, Calvin Klein, O'neil, Neiman Marcus and Hush LA among others. She can do her own hair makeup and styling and has an extensive wardrobe comprised of casual wear, high fashion garments, lingerie, bikinis, jewelry, hats, boots and heels. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

chellemodelnyc.description: Michelle Bobe is a New York City based fashion/commercial model of mixed ethnicity. She is represented non-exclusively by Americana Models. She freelances and books allot of her own fashion jobs. Always aiming to further her modeling career, she is continually testing with high fashion photographers both in NYC and overseas. Being only 5”6” in. tall she is living proof that with enough motivation and the right networking, it is possible to "work" as a fashion model in the toughest market in the world... NYC.

_jhaza.description: Jhaza Tanner (pronounced: Jah-Zay) has been modeling since she was 13 years old and it has been her passion ever since. She takes direction well, works well with others, has a proficient runway walk, sense of style, communication skills, and loves being in front of the camera. The type of modeling she is capable of is runway, print, editorial, swimwear, sport/fitness, product, and much more. Modeling is her outlet, a way to express herself by becoming something or someone else. She is known for her professionalism and determination. Available for fashion and print projects.

krystalnbailey.description: For the past several years, Krystal Nichole has made a name for herself in the modeling industry and has had the honor of working with renowned photographers and international brands. The Panamanian-American model's strong features and unique look has often been compared to that of the great Naomi Campbell. Krystal has done editorials for numerous magazines including Essence, Ebony, Vibe, Cosmopolitan, New Beauty, and Seventeen and has appeared in adverts and catalogs for companies such as Lexus, Pantene, Bare Minerals, Soft & Beautiful, and many more. She has also appeared on several book covers and her Lexus campaign has graced the nations top magazines and nationwide billboards. Krystal Nichole has been focused on building her brand, entrepreneurship, and philanthropy. Launching small businesses, inspiring others through fitness and health, and giving back to her community is what makes Krystal truly shine.

i_am_ansar_shabazz.description: Ansar Shabazz is a model based in Atlanta. His work experience includes fashion photoshoots and participation in events. Ansar has modeled for brands such as H&M and Hugo Boss among others. Available for fashion and print projects internationally.

amandagift.description: Amanda Gift is a professional model and actress based in Huntington Beach. Her work includes photoshoots for numerous magazines, calendars and publications as well as Film/TV Appearances. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

susanncoffey.description: Susan is an independent New Jersey Model. She is available to shoot in the tri-state area.

ginnyconnor.description: Ginny is Former 2012 Tucson12 model/student at the University of Arizona. She aspires to become a psychologist, but is extremely passionate and enthusiastic about a career in modeling aswell. Recently moved from Seattle to Los Angeles and is looking to network, connect and collaborate with professional, experienced and talented photographers as well as other companies/organizations. She'd like to expand and diversify her portfolio to get represented by a reputable modeling agency. Available for fashion and print projects.

misslhommedieu.description: Amanda Lynn L’hommedieu is a model based in Las Vegas, USA. She is an experienced model that has had the opportunity to travel all over the world. Her work experience includes multiple fashion, swimwear and glamour photoshoots as well as promotions. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

sydneyamaler.description: Sydney A. Maler is a Southern-California grown model currently based in San Diego. Modeling is her passion. She is an avid beach bum, and would always rather be in a bikini, bare foot with wild, unruly hair. She believes there are too many places and things that are unexplored and experienced. She loves the weird quirky places that having such a creative job takes her. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

gemmaleefarrell.description: Gemma Lee Farrell is a New Zealand Born Model, Living in Los Angeles. She has been Playboy Playmate Miss November 2013 and her work experience includes numerous promotions and fashion events. Available for fashion and print projects internationally.

nattanpires.description: Nattan Pires is a brazilian model living in the United States. He is interested in collaborating with other professionals. Available for fashion and print projects.

kourtneyreppert.description: Kourtney is an American model dubbed Philadelphia's Hottest Sports Babe & "Model Of The Year" for the Philadelphia Phillies & Flyers. A lifelong athlete, she fell into sports modeling naturally and has been featured by Sports Illustrated, Maxim Radio, and FOX Sports. stoli_thewna.description: Tewna Stolichnaya is a model based in Netherlands . She has studied economics and administration.Her work experience includes fashion photoshoots and participation in events. Available for fashion and print projects

gulseamine.description: Amine Gulse is a model from Izmir, Turkey. She has wan the Miss Turkey (2014) pageant. She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

barisfit9.description: Baris Murat Yağcı was born in Alacatı, Izmir on the 21st January. He studied at Izmir Private Turkish college in Izmir. He finished his high school in Istanbul and continues to study at Bahçesehir University in Istanbul, where he currently lives.

aghahooman.description: Hooman Hosseini is a model and fitness trainer based in Ankara. He is of Spain and Iranian origin and his interests include Boxing & UFC. He is available for fashion and print projects.

gizemkock.description: Gizem Kocak is a model based in Instabul Turkey. She has won Elidor Miss international (2014). She is available for fashion and print projects internationally.

manzi_axel.description: Manzi Ron Axel is a Rwandan model currently based in Ankara. Manzi was the 2nd runner up in the Mister Kigali Beauty contest in2013. His modeling experience includes small fashion gigs in Kigali and He has participated in one fashion and runway show and has never modeled for any known brand

not_wish_just_do.description: Modeling, for me, isn't about being beautiful but creating something interesting for people to look at and think about.

valeria_gurevich.description: Valeria gurevich is an Israeli Model (born October 12, 1991), Her mother, Irina Gurevich, is Russian, and her Father, Radge Gurevich, is half-Korean and half-Japanese. Valeria has been modelling since the age of 13.

jennytokarev.description: Jenny Tokarev is an International Fashion model having modeled more than 10 years for leading brands such as: Sony Ericsson, Indola, Diesel Jeans, TV commercials, etc. TV comedy program guides: "Fun Night" She has participated in Big Brother Realty 2009 - Israel. She is experienced in fashion productions, TV (guidance, television programs, commercials) and theater, having worked in South Africa, London, Milan, Russia, and Israel. She is available for fashion, print and commercial projects internationally.
